lib.nbt

Class SyncTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • lib.nbt.Tag
      • lib.nbt.SyncTag

  • public class SyncTag
extends Tag
    An extension of Tag used internally by NBTTree to provide a link between the tree model and the NBT data model, particularly elements within NBTLists and NBTArrayLists. Not intended for direct use.
    Author:
    Kyrillos Tawadros
    See Also:
    NBTTree
